s life-or-death and the equity gap is recipe-author's own framing of the patients-with-greatest-unmet-need-have-least-access-to-digital-tools as life-safety-acute. The recipe contains explicit `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Expert review S2 (HIGH) -->` and `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Expert review A1 (HIGH) -->` markers anticipating this finding.
